snippet.title: Pirates of the Silver Bullet: Amber Heard's Self-Inflicted Family Law Ricochet
snippet.description:
In Episode 3 of the video podcast - The Respondent - Greg exposes Amber Heard's #MeToo playbook.

Janice Fiamengo joins for a live Q&A after the episode. This all kicks off on Sunday, July 19th, at 1:00 p.m. Pacific Time on thinkspot. Register here: https://www.thinkspot.com/event_signu...
